## Yandex Cloud Translate
## 1) Provide either IAM token or OAuth token (server can exchange OAuth -> IAM)
## 2) Get your folder id
## 3) Copy this file to ".env" and fill the values, then restart: npm start

## Option A (recommended if you already have it):
YC_IAM_TOKEN=

## Option A2 (recommended): API key (Translate API)
YC_API_KEY=

## Option B (you can paste your OAuth token here; server will exchange it):
YC_OAUTH_TOKEN=

YC_FOLDER_ID=

